subtitleNullable: Monthly Import Value of Coffee for 32 years
descriptionNullable:
Brazil is the world's largest coffee-producing country, but it still imports a large amount of coffee. The dataset includes the monthly value of Coffee imports in Brazil for 32.5 years from Jan 1990 to June 2022.
The data is taken from the United States Department of Agriculture, Foreign Agriculture Services website.
